  <title>GLib.FileTest</title>
  <p>A test to perform on a file using <link xref="GLib.file_test"/>.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>FileTest.IS_REGULAR</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the file is a regular file
    (not a directory). Note that this test will also return <code>true</code>
    if the tested file is a symlink to a regular file.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileTest.IS_SYMLINK</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the file is a symlink.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileTest.IS_DIR</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the file is a directory.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileTest.IS_EXECUTABLE</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the file is executable.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileTest.EXISTS</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the file exists. It may or may not
    be a regular file.</p>
</item>
</terms>
